  <ResearchGuidenceSystem.ResearchLabel>全球定位系统</ResearchGuidenceSystem.ResearchLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: Upgrade -->
  <ResearchMEPS.ProjTypeLabel>升级组件</ResearchMEPS.ProjTypeLabel>
  <!-- EN: The Modular Electric Power System (MEPS) is an ultra-capacitor that can interface with the power delivery system of any Rimatomics energy weapon to boost its maximum power, the extra power may be handled differently by each energy weapon -->
  <ResearchMEPS.ResearchDesc>模块化电力系统是一种超级电容器，可以与任何「边缘核能」系列能量武器的供电系统相连接，以提升其最大功率，每种能量武器的提升效果不同。</ResearchMEPS.ResearchDesc>
  <!-- EN: You can now produce MEPS modules at the Rimatomics machining table, to install them into a Rimatomics energy weapon select the weapon and toggle the MEPS button on\n\nThe MEPS must be manually installed in each new building -->
  <ResearchMEPS.ResearchDescDisc>您现在可以在「边缘核能」加工台制作模块化电力系统，并将其安装到「边缘核能」系列能量武器中，选择能量武器并指定安装模块化电力系统。</ResearchMEPS.ResearchDescDisc>
