  <ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ProjTypeLabel>升级组件</ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ProjTypeLabel>
  <!-- EN: The Obelisks laser can be split using a beam splitter, the secondary beam is tuned to a particular wavelength and polarization state which disables personal shields, the primary beam is delayed by a fraction of a second and then delivered with full power to the target -->
  <ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ResearchDesc>光明石碑可以使用电子束分裂器对激光进行分光处理，次级光束被调谐到特定的波长和极化状态，用于击破护盾，主光束延迟一秒到达，攻击已无护盾保护的目标。</ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ResearchDesc>
  <!-- EN: You can now produce Beam splitters's at the Rimatomics machining table, to install them into an Obelisk, select the Obelisk and designate the Beam splitter for installation -->
  <ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ResearchDescDisc>您现在可以在「边缘核能」加工台制作电子束分裂器，并将其安装到光明石碑中，选择光明石碑并指定安装电子束分裂器。</ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ResearchDescDisc>
  <!-- EN: Obelisk Beam Splitter -->
  <ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ResearchLabel>电子束分裂器</ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.ResearchLabel>
  <!-- EN: Breaks shields and spreads the damage -->
  <ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.stats.0>破坏护盾并造成伤害</ResearchObelisk_BeamSplitter.stats.0>
  
